    Interface for the exhibit of the art gallery.

    This interface models the exhibits data related to the management of the ticket office, such as the number of daily tickets and the total income resulting from the sale of the tickets.

    This interface models a generic purchase of one or more tickets for an exhibit.
    ISalesManagement
    This interface models the act of selling tickets and cashing in the payments.

    This interface models a ticket.
